size firms with the advantages of a full service HR department.\r\n\r\nWe provide our clients and employees with more freedom of choice in a benefits package that goes beyond what they could expect even working at a larger company.\r\n\r\nSome may call it old-fashioned, but we are proud of the fact that when one of our clients or employees calls us on a particular issue, they find an Abel employee ready to help them on the other end of the phone. No electronic voices. No menu maze to get caught in and confused by. No voicemail bouncing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Business, Simple!</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_5 prefix_1 is_grid\" style=\"background: #eee; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 10px 20px 30px;\">\r\n<h2>Client/Customer Login</h2>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\"><form style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\" action=\"/wp/myinc/login.asp\" method=\"POST\" name=\"loginForm\">\r\n<table id=\"login-table\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Login:</td>\r\n<td><input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" /></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Password:</td>\r\n<td><input type=\"password\" name=\"password\" /></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>User:</td>\r\n<td><select name=\"logintype\"> <option value=\"a\"> Abel Associate</option> <option value=\"c\">  Client</option> <option value=\"e\">  Employee</option> </select></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><input class=\"art-button\" type=\"submit\" name=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" /></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</form></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_7 is_grid\">\r\n<h2>Services</h2>\r\nWe provide the following services to small &amp; medium businesses.\r\n<div class=\"grid_5 alpha is_grid\">\r\n<ul class=\"contentList arrow\">\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://think.yoshimoshi.com/services/payroll/\">Payroll and Related Taxes</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://think.yoshimoshi.com/services/employee-benefits-management/\">Employee Benefits Management</a></li>\r\n	<l