assment allegations, wage and hour compliance, discriminatory practice charges and many other employment related issues.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<strong>Payroll Programs and Taxes</strong>\r\n&nbsp;\r\nThe IRS has reported that one out of every three employers has been charged for a payroll tax mistake, with total penalties reaching into the billions of dollars. And, given the ever-changing nature of tax regulations, it’s easy to make an error that can grossly affect your bottom line.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLearn more about our complete range of Payroll Programs and Tax services to help manage your payroll quickly and efficiently.\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<strong>This list represents some of the services provided by Abel</strong>:\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Preparation and distribution of payroll checks</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible payroll input (fax, e-mail, Web)</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated payroll representative</li>\r\n	<li>Detailed management reports</li>\r\n	<li>Custom reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Sick, vacation and PTO tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Certified payroll processing</li>\r\n	<li>State and federal deposits and filings (quarterly and year-end)</li>\r\n	<li>Direct deposit</li>\r\n	<li>W-2 preparation and distribution</li>\r\n	<li>Processing of employee liens, loans and garnishments</li>\r\n	<li>Labor distribution and job costing</li>\r\n	<li>Time clock interface (Web-enabled or swipe system)</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','93-revision-7','','','2012-06-05 04:09:49','2012-06-05 04:09:49','',93,'http://think.yoshimoshi.com/93-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(388,2,'2012-06-20 05:09:15','2012-06-20 05:09:15','<strong><a href=\"http://think.yoshimoshi.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/payroll2_edited-v3.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-380\" title=\"payroll2_edited-v3\" src=\"http://think.yoshimoshi.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/payroll2_edited-v3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"330\" /></a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-386